    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Good records management practices should assist authorities to meet their duties under the Act. If records are easy to locate then requests can be dealt with quickly. Records management is covered by a Code of Practice. The Code provides guidance on records management policies, records management training and the keeping, management and destruction of records, both paper based and electronic. QMU has a records management policy to adopt best practice in this area.</p>]]></Value>
